00:05:43.390 --> 00:05:48.560
This is one edge of the shell,
that's the other shell.

00:05:48.560 --> 00:05:52.020
We already figured out that
the width of the shell is dx.

00:05:52.020 --> 00:05:55.410
The height is 4 minus x
squared, the top function minus

00:05:55.410 --> 00:05:58.070
the bottom function because of
the distance between the two.

00:05:58.070 --> 00:06:01.200
And then what's the
radius going to be?

00:06:01.200 --> 00:06:05.040
What's the radius of
that shell going to be?

00:06:05.040 --> 00:06:07.570
Well, is it going to be just x?

00:06:07.570 --> 00:06:08.220
Is it just going to be x value?

00:06:08.220 --> 00:06:12.580
No, the x value will tell you
the distance from the y-axis to

00:06:12.580 --> 00:06:16.750
that shell, and it's going to
be from minus 2 to the e value.

00:06:16.750 --> 00:06:22.630
So it's going to be
essentially 2 plus x.

00:06:22.630 --> 00:06:25.220
That's going to be the
radius at any point.

00:06:25.220 --> 00:06:28.030
And this is where we diverge
from what we've done before.

00:06:28.030 --> 00:06:31.630
Before the radius was just
x, but now it's 2 plus x.

00:06:31.630 --> 00:06:35.280
So what's the circumference
of each shell going to be?

00:06:35.280 --> 00:06:39.460
Well circumference is
equal to 2 pi r, and

00:06:39.460 --> 00:06:40.890
our radius is 2 plus x.

00:06:40.890 --> 00:06:48.690
So it's 2 pi times 2 plus
x, which equals 4 pi

00:06:48.690 --> 00:06:54.310
plus 4 pi plus 2 pi x.

00:06:54.310 --> 00:06:55.840
That's the circumference.

00:06:55.840 --> 00:06:57.940
And then what's the
surface area of this?

00:06:57.940 --> 00:07:00.960
Well it's going to be the
circumference times the height.

00:07:00.960 --> 00:07:04.630
So surface area is
equal to that.

00:07:04.630 --> 00:07:12.180
The circumference 4 pi plus 2
pi x, all of that times the

00:07:12.180 --> 00:07:17.220
height-- times 4
minus x squared.

00:07:17.220 --> 00:07:19.540
And let's see if we
can foil this out or

00:07:19.540 --> 00:07:20.870
distribute this out.

00:07:20.870 --> 00:07:24.810
So 4 pi times 4 is 16 pi.

00:07:24.810 --> 00:07:31.580
4 pi minus x squared
minus 4 pi x squared.

00:07:31.580 --> 00:07:38.040
2 pi x times 4 plus 8 pi x, and
then 2 pi x times minus x

00:07:38.040 --> 00:07:43.030
squared, so that's minus
2 pi x to the third.

00:07:43.030 --> 00:07:44.980
So that's the surface
area of each ring.

00:07:44.980 --> 00:07:48.820
And then if we want the volume
of each shell, essentially

00:07:48.820 --> 00:07:50.890
we multiply it times
the width, the dx.

00:07:56.390 --> 00:07:58.220
So that's the volume of
each shell, and if we want

00:07:58.220 --> 00:08:03.180
the volume of all the
shells, we sum them up.

